extendedInfo.description: Got a cleaning problem? Worried about ingredients inside your cleaning products? This guide is for you. We'll help you make wholesome choices for your home and help educate you about how to read labels so you can understand the potential risks in many cleaning products. Download the Earth Friendly Products Guide application and become a green cleaning expert. As a leader in green cleaning supplies, Earth Friendly Products has ECOS, the #1 top-selling green laundry detergent in the world and Wave, the first pH neutral dishwashing detergent on the market. With a wide variety of products available in major supermarkets and grocery retailers around the world, Earth Friendly Products continues to provide the safest and healthiest cleaning options for families and the environment.
